videos.description: Virginia shows off the good ball movement, finally landing in the hands of London Perrantes, who drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Perrantes drills the three after some strong UVA passing

videos.description: Quentin Snider made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Quentin Snider knocks down a three to cut the UVA lead to 6
Mamadi Diakite gets the steal and throws it down on the other end

videos.description: Longon Perrantes throws the perfect alley-oop to Darius Thompson, who cuts to the basket and soars in for the two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Perrantes connects with Thompson on perfect alley-oop) 2016/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Perrantes connects with Thompson on perfect alley-oop

videos.description: Early in the second half, Darius Thompson feeds Jack Salt in transition for the slam and Virginia goes up 40-25 on Louisville.
videos.headline: UVa's Jack Salt throws down dunk in transition

videos.description: Anas Mahmoud made Dunk. Assisted by Quentin Snider.
videos.headline: Anas Mahmoud catches the alley oop and throws it down for the and one

videos.description: Isaiah Wilkins steals the ball from Louisville and Mamadi Diakite gets it on the other end for the dunk to put Virginia up by 21 points.
videos.headline: Virginia strips the ball and goes in for easy slam

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Anas Mahmoud.
videos.headline: Donovan Mitchell knocks down the three as LOUISVILLE tries to erase UVA's double digit lead

videos.description: London Perrantes records nine points and seven assists in No. 12 Virginia's 61-53 victory over No. 6 Louisville.
videos.headline: Virginia tops Louisville in ACC opener
